| Severity | Count | Top Issue |
|----------|-------|-----------|
| 🔴 Critical | 2 | `String.Split` + LINQ allocations in word truncator |
| 🟡 Moderate | 3 | Double-alloc substring, unsealed classes, List\<char\> lookup |
| ℹ️ Info | 0 | — |

